html:
Field

Description

Minimum required balance

The minimum amount that must be maintained in the account.

Withdrawal limits

The number or amount of withdrawals allowed within a specified period.

Interest rate, %

Annual interest rate applied to the account balance.

APY, %

Annual Percentage Yield for the account.

Interest payout frequency

How often interest is paid out, for example, monthly, quarterly.

Primary checking account

The main checking account associated with the savings or money market account.
